      "raw_text_preview": "MOIL LIMITED\n(Formerly MANGANESE ORE (INDIA) LIMITED)\nA Govt. of India Enterprise\nMOIL BHAVAN, 1A, Katol Road,\nNAGPUR-440 013\nPhone: 0712-2591850, 2806100\nFax: 0712-2590644 Website : moil.nic.in\n02.05.2026\nSub: Price & Availability of Manganese Ore for Direct Sale for quarter Apr-Jun, 2026.\nDear Sir,\nAttached, is the Company’s prices of various grades of Manganese Ore for the month of May,2026 with\neffect from 01/05/2026 during the quarter April-June,2026 for supply of Manganese Ore. Please note\nthat the attached file is password protected and you will be required to use the password to open the\nfile. The password has already been communicated to the existing buyers. In-case the password e-mail\ncommunication has not been received, kindly contact Mr. Harpreet Singh, DGM(Marketing), Mr.Satish\nTiwari, AGM(Marketing), Mr.Amitabha Mitra, Chief Manager (Marketing), Ms.Pooja Upadhaya,\nManager(Marketing) and Ms. Natasha Jaiswal, Manager (Marketing) on Phone No. 8956756444,\n9766914406, 9049422219,8605012737, 8800512471 respectively, and request for the password\ncommunication immediately.\nCertain quantities of Manganese Ore are available for Direct Sale. Interested buyers are requested to\nsu"
